description: Erection of a residential development comprising of 165 flats in a part 10, 11, 20 and 21 storey building comprising ten studio, seventy seven 1- bedroomed, sixty eight 2- bedroomed and ten 3- bedroomed build to rent residential units with 11 car parking spaces at lower ground level, new vehicle access from Sutton Court Road and internal cycle stores, refuse and recycling facilities, plant accommodation and associated hard and soft landscaping.
